section>\r\n\t\t<section id=\"design\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"ttl_h\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"c\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"t\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>D</span><span>E</span><span>S</span><span>I</span><span>G</span><span>N</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img img_scale\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../bin/page/uniform/img/design.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"pc_view_i\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../bin/page/uniform/img/design_sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"sp_view_i\">\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"copy bar_txt\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../bin/page/uniform/img/design_copy.svg\" alt=\"チーム全体を引き立てる\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"txt fadein\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"t1\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t現場の仕事はチームで行うもの。<br>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t一人ではなく全体で見たときに引き立つ<br class=\"sp_view_i\">デザインをテーマに<br class=\"pc_view_i\"><span>Uniform Circus <br class=\"sp_view_i\">BEAMS</span>に制作いただきました。\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t</section>\r\n\t\t<section id=\"point\">\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"container\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"ttl_h\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"c\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"t\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>P</span><span>O</span><span>I</span><span>N</span><span>T</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"num\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>Point</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>01</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"txts\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"t1\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tアパレルブランドによるデザイン\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"t2\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tアウトドアウェアからインスパイアされた<br class=\"pc_view_i\">2色の切り返しをつかった配色。\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../bin/page/uniform/img/point1.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\